room_title: Escape room "Hole in the Wall" by Hint Hunter Puzzle Rooms in Biloxi
review: I just did the Hole in the Wall escape room with my husband and we had an absolute blast! We did not make it out, but we were very close. Our host was great and the room was challenging enough to be super fun, but not overly frustrating. We will definitely go back!

room_title: Escape room "Hole in the Wall" by Hint Hunter Puzzle Rooms in Biloxi
review: Totally a newbie-friendly place! Loved Jeffrey and how attentive he was. We did take the entire 30 minutes but somehow felt good about it! It was fun! I will be back!
